## Your First Project

The best way to start is by comparing a SQL query to a Spark DataFrame operation.

### The Task
Find the average salary of employees per department.

### The SQL Way

```sql
SELECT dept_id, AVG(salary) 
FROM employees 
GROUP BY dept_id;
```

### The Spark Scala Way (The New Way)

```scala
val df = spark.read.json("employees.json")
df.groupBy("dept_id")
  .avg("salary") 
  .show()
```

